30:15.596 --> 30:17.859
Thanks for
saving my spot.

30:17.903 --> 30:19.992
Yeah.

30:20.035 --> 30:24.387
♪♪

30:24.431 --> 30:25.954
So, uh,
what's the deal?

30:25.998 --> 30:27.869
Ah,
just a rando spot check.

30:27.913 --> 30:30.654
All the Fortune 500s do it,
Rip Van Winkle.

30:30.698 --> 30:33.962
[ Chuckles ][ Cellphone rings ]

30:34.006 --> 30:41.143
♪♪

30:41.187 --> 30:43.885
[ Cellphone rings ]

30:43.929 --> 30:47.889
Gap in the line there,
Benmeister.

30:47.933 --> 30:49.717
You know what?

30:49.760 --> 30:52.067
I'm gonna use
the head.

30:52.111 --> 31:02.077
♪♪

31:02.121 --> 31:08.867
♪♪

31:08.910 --> 31:10.912
What are
you doing here?

31:10.956 --> 31:14.220
Corporate espionage is a felony,
Mr. Stone.

31:14.263 --> 31:16.222
Where is it?
Shoe?

31:16.265 --> 31:18.920
No. Thermos.

31:18.964 --> 31:19.921
That's clever.

31:19.965 --> 31:22.924
Thing is,
I'm pretty clever too.

31:22.968 --> 31:25.057
♪♪

31:25.100 --> 31:27.668
How did you...?I'm a deputy director

31:27.711 --> 31:29.888
of the National Security Agency,
Ben.

31:29.931 --> 31:32.368
It's, you know,
kind of what we do.

31:32.412 --> 31:33.892
Hand it over.

31:33.935 --> 31:35.894
Come on.
You don't understand.

31:35.937 --> 31:37.721
This data
can get me to the detainees,

31:37.765 --> 31:39.549
which might be the only way
to protect my son.

31:39.593 --> 31:40.986
This is not
a negotiation.

31:41.029 --> 31:42.552
You can either
hand over the flash drive,

31:42.596 --> 31:44.076
or you can be
under arrest.

31:44.119 --> 31:45.338
You're a math guy.

31:45.381 --> 31:47.644
Not much
of a calculus.

31:47.688 --> 31:57.567
♪♪

31:57.611 --> 31:59.395
Vance...

31:59.439 --> 32:01.571
Vance,
you have to find them!

32:01.615 --> 32:04.096
Vance!

32:04.139 --> 32:08.927
♪♪

32:12.843 --> 32:15.629
[ Indistinct conversations ]

32:15.672 --> 32:21.417
[ Murmuring ]

32:21.461 --> 32:31.340
♪♪

32:31.384 --> 32:40.959
♪♪

32:41.002 --> 32:43.831
♪♪

32:43.874 --> 32:46.268
This guy's probably
long gone by now.

32:46.312 --> 32:48.444
♪♪

