Go faster!
Go faster!

32:54.059 --> 32:56.191
Is this
what I think it is?

32:56.235 --> 32:57.410
Is it the voices?

32:57.453 --> 33:00.674
It's different this time.
I can feel it.

33:00.717 --> 33:03.068
[ Breathing heavily ]

33:03.111 --> 33:11.946
♪♪

33:11.990 --> 33:16.646
[ Heart beating]

33:16.690 --> 33:17.734
Turn left!

33:17.778 --> 33:20.041
[ Tires squeal, horns honk ]

33:20.085 --> 33:30.051
♪♪

33:30.095 --> 33:33.750
♪♪

33:33.794 --> 33:37.058
[ Keys jingle ]

33:37.102 --> 33:39.408
♪♪

33:39.452 --> 33:40.801
[ Breathing heavily ]

33:40.844 --> 33:42.759
Right. Right.

33:42.803 --> 33:44.413
[ Tires squeal ]

33:44.457 --> 33:45.980
What's it saying?

33:46.024 --> 33:47.721
It's not
saying anything.

33:47.764 --> 33:50.593
It's a heartbeat.Maybe it's just
yourheartbeat.

33:50.637 --> 33:51.942
No, it's not,
it wouldn't -- it just --

33:51.986 --> 33:53.422
Wait, it was there,
and now it's not.

33:53.466 --> 33:54.728
It's not there anymore.

33:54.771 --> 33:57.122
It stopped.
Stop the car!

33:57.165 --> 33:59.776
[ Tires screech ]

33:59.820 --> 34:08.829
♪♪

34:08.872 --> 34:10.700
♪♪

34:10.744 --> 34:12.267
Aah!
Give me the money.

34:12.311 --> 34:14.748
No, get off me.Give me the money!

34:14.791 --> 34:16.054
It's all I have!

34:16.097 --> 34:17.794
[ Bottle shatters ]

34:17.838 --> 34:19.187
Man: Get off me!

34:19.231 --> 34:20.275
Aah!

34:20.319 --> 34:21.494
♪♪

34:21.537 --> 34:23.800
[ Handcuffs clicking ]

34:23.844 --> 34:28.718
♪♪

34:28.762 --> 34:30.894
That might've been
your best yet.

34:30.938 --> 34:33.245
Eh, I just think
we need more height.

34:33.288 --> 34:35.638
Oh, do you, hot shot?
Seriously.

34:35.682 --> 34:38.424
Like,
a legit simulation.
Mm.

34:38.467 --> 34:40.730
[ Door opens ]

34:45.822 --> 34:48.782
Successful mission.

34:48.825 --> 34:50.218
Thanks for taking her.

34:50.262 --> 34:58.748
♪♪

34:58.792 --> 35:00.576
Bye.

35:00.620 --> 35:05.190
♪♪

35:05.233 --> 35:07.627
Grace:
So, was it fun?

35:07.670 --> 35:10.238
Yeah.

35:10.282 --> 35:12.240
♪♪

35:12.284 --> 35:14.460
[ Door closes ]

35:14.503 --> 35:21.989
♪♪

35:22.032 --> 35:23.556
[ Gearshift clicks ]

35:23.599 --> 35:29.605
♪♪

35:29.649 --> 35:32.478
Danny: You're a good man
to let her stick with this.

35:32.521 --> 35:33.827
She did great.

35:33.870 --> 35:35.045
No doubt.

35:35.089 --> 35:37.570
So,
how much longer?
I'm sorry?

35:37.613 --> 35:39.659
You're training for a climb.
When's the climb?

35:39.702 --> 35:42.357
Oh, summer.

35:42.401 --> 35:44.185
Gotcha.

35:44.229 --> 35:47.014
I'm not gonna get
in your way, Ben.

35:47.057 --> 35:48.842
Olive's not my kid.

35:48.885 --> 35:51.149
But I stepped in
when you were gone,

35:51.192 --> 35:54.152
and I care about her.

35:54.195 --> 35:57.546
When she comes to me,
I can't turn her away.

35:57.590 --> 35:59.200
♪♪

35:59.244 --> 36:01.855
Nice to see you,
Danny.

36:01.898 --> 36:08.427
♪♪

36:12.561 --> 36:15.042
[ Door beeps ]

36:17.305 --> 36:18.741
We got him.

36:18.785 --> 36:21.309
He walked
because of me.

36:21.353 --> 36:24.138
If you hadn't caught him,
he might've --
But we did.

36:24.182 --> 36:27.446
And when you ID him,
he's gonna go away for good.

36:27.489 --> 36:29.622
[ Horn honks ]

36:29.665 --> 36:35.758
[ Heart beating]

36:35.802 --> 36:38.108
I'm assuming
you didn't hear that.

36:38.152 --> 36:40.546
The subway?

36:40.589 --> 36:44.985
[ Heart beating]

36:45.028 --> 36:52.993
♪♪

36:53.036 --> 37:00.043
♪♪

37:00.087 --> 37:03.264
♪♪

37:03.308 --> 37:05.614
How did
you know Evie?

37:05.658 --> 37:07.050
You knew Evie?

37:07.094 --> 37:08.835
She was
my best friend.

37:08.878 --> 37:10.445
Told you
I almost died.

37:10.489 --> 37:14.188
Congestive heart failure --
I needed a transplant.

37:14.232 --> 37:17.017
She was my donor.

37:17.060 --> 37:27.027
♪♪

37:27.070 --> 37:33.120
♪♪

