37:53.358 --> 37:57.840
♪ Life is anything but fair

37:57.884 --> 38:01.017
♪ Life is anything but fair

38:01.061 --> 38:04.934
♪ Oh, oh, oh, oh

38:04.978 --> 38:07.197
♪ Whoo, hoo, hoo, hoo

38:07.241 --> 38:12.028
♪ Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh

38:12.072 --> 38:13.856
I'm worried
about Evie.

38:13.900 --> 38:16.337
♪ Just as soon
as they turn older ♪She's been gone so long.

38:16.381 --> 38:19.645
You don't need to worry.
