I saw Evie. She's okay.♪ He'll come and sweep them
off their feet ♪

38:22.604 --> 38:24.911
She's okay.

38:24.954 --> 38:26.347
She's okay.

38:26.391 --> 38:29.568
♪ It's only making me
feel smaller ♪

38:29.611 --> 38:32.353
Look at that.

38:32.397 --> 38:35.051
♪ All the hidden love
beneath ♪Hey, bud.

38:35.095 --> 38:37.706
Feeling okay?Did the secret work?

38:37.750 --> 38:39.012
Did you find the man?

38:39.055 --> 38:40.274
Almost, buddy,

38:40.318 --> 38:42.232
but it shouldn't be
too much longer.

38:42.276 --> 38:44.234
I had a big
breakthrough today.

38:44.278 --> 38:47.063
Then someone bad
got in my way,

38:47.107 --> 38:51.285
but I promise
I'm not gonna give up.

38:51.329 --> 38:52.808
You don't
have to worry.

38:53.983 --> 38:56.725
He's not a bad guy,
Dad.

38:56.769 --> 38:58.945
Not anymore.

38:58.988 --> 39:06.256
♪♪

39:06.300 --> 39:12.175
[ Cellphone ringing ]

39:12.219 --> 39:13.699
[ Cellphone clicks ]

39:13.742 --> 39:15.091
Vance.

39:15.135 --> 39:16.658
Powell: I've got a team
on standby.

39:16.702 --> 39:18.268
Anything you've got
off Stone,

39:18.312 --> 39:20.401
they're ready
to jump in.

39:20.445 --> 39:23.099
No,
I didn't get anything.

39:23.143 --> 39:24.753
He was clean.

39:24.797 --> 39:27.930
[ Cellphone beeps ]

39:27.974 --> 39:34.023
♪♪

39:34.067 --> 39:36.983
How's Cal?

39:37.026 --> 39:39.246
He's okay.

39:39.289 --> 39:42.467
You,
maybe not so much.

39:42.510 --> 39:43.859
♪♪

39:43.903 --> 39:46.732
I need to understand.

39:46.775 --> 39:50.518
The callings,
what's happening with Cal.

39:50.562 --> 39:56.132
I want to believe
there's a -- a reason,

39:56.176 --> 39:59.701
but it requires
this leap of faith,

39:59.745 --> 40:02.008
and I can't...

40:02.051 --> 40:04.619
♪♪

40:04.663 --> 40:07.274
I can't trust
what I don't understand.

40:07.317 --> 40:14.629
♪♪

40:14.673 --> 40:18.198
I don't understand it
any more than you do.

40:18.241 --> 40:24.204
But I take that leap
and I follow the calling.

40:24.247 --> 40:26.859
And I feel
a little better.

40:26.902 --> 40:28.513
♪♪

40:28.556 --> 40:30.515
For the first time
since Evie,

40:30.558 --> 40:33.561
I feel like
I might just be okay.

40:33.605 --> 40:35.389
♪♪

40:35.433 --> 40:38.044
That's why I was drawn
to the boy,

40:38.087 --> 40:40.525
to Evie's heart.

40:40.568 --> 40:43.658
I had to know
that the callings were right,

40:43.702 --> 40:46.139
that it is
all connected.

40:46.182 --> 40:47.662
Connected to what?

40:47.706 --> 40:50.448
To us,
to -- to each other.

40:50.491 --> 40:54.060
That's what
all of this is for.

40:54.103 --> 40:55.931
It has to be.

40:55.975 --> 41:02.590
♪♪

41:02.634 --> 41:05.071
Great.

41:05.114 --> 41:06.768
You got a sign.

41:06.812 --> 41:09.075
Where's mine?

41:09.118 --> 41:12.905
♪♪

41:12.948 --> 41:16.996
Ben,
when did Cal draw that?

41:17.039 --> 41:19.564
Ben:
The other day. Why?

41:19.607 --> 41:21.696
♪♪

41:21.740 --> 41:25.134
That's Carlos
